<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-734] Commons DBCP parameters should be configurable. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-734</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per conversation on the users mailing list &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; it would be nice to make the connection pool used for unit tests configurable. Some environments are not well suited to handle the current list of defaults. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://openjpa.markmail.org/message/uctj54wt733wxtp4?q=milosz&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://openjpa.markmail.org/message/uctj54wt733wxtp4?q=milosz&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
or &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://n2.nabble.com/Test-suite-slow-on-DB2-td1115993.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://n2.nabble.com/Test-suite-slow-on-DB2-td1115993.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
